  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Send Transaction: If type amount, e.g 123 and later select a recipient from Contacts then typed amount is cleaned (becomes 0.000)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nTyped amount is in the field\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nField lost types amount and contains 0.000\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- open wallet\r\n- tap Send\r\n- in Amount type 123\r\n- tap on Recipient\r\n- Select from contact Jarrad\r\n- check amount on Send screen: in develop it's still 123, in this PR it's 0.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: develop \r\n* Operating System: \r\nReal device iPhone 6s, iOs 10.3.3\r\nReal device Samsung Galaxy S6, android 6.0.1",
